Race.SpecificTitle: Council Member -- District 2, Town of Haynesville
PW Law Enforcement District -- 12 Mills - Sheriff - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Law Enforcement District of the Parish of Claiborne, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a tax of twelve (12) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $1,568,200 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2019 and ending with the year 2028, for the purpose of providing additional funds for the District?
